By Azuka Ogujiuba Nigeria’s leading film production companies, Inkblot productions and Filmone Distribution, recently held the premiere for the most anticipated movie of the year, New Money, at the Imax Cinemas, Lekki, Lagos. Directed by Tope Oshin; New Money stars Dakore Egbuson-Akande, Kate Henshaw, Blossom Chukwujekwu, Jemima Osunde, Falz, Osas Ighodaro-Ajibade, Wofai, Wale Ojo, Adeolu Adefarasin, Daniel Etim Effiong, Femi Branch, Bikiya Graham-Douglas, and Damola Layonu. The movie is scheduled for release in Cinemas nationwide from March 23, 2018. These are some of the people at the premiere.